dresses.title: Corey Lynn Calter Shoulder
dresses.description: With experience gained in opera houses, Broadway shows and New York's punk scene, Corey Lynn Calter's eponymous line is defined by original prints, flattering cuts, and punchy hues that are inspired by her vast and varied background.
